    <td align="center" style="font-weight:bold;">Introduction</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>
      <p>The purpose of this program is to help candidates familiarize with the format and operation of the Computerized Written Test of driving Test.</p>
      <p>In the actual test, candidates can only use touch screen devices to give answers.  Candidates can practise touch screen features by using the Kiosks located at our 3 Schools located at Shatin, Hong Kong Island and Yuen Long.</p>
      <p>There are 14 groups of questions in the Trial Test, each group contains 20 questions.  The questions in the Trial Test are for reference only and may not be applied to real world situation.  However, in the actual test, candidates will receive their result slips at the respective Appointment Offices in about 15 minutes after they complete the tests.</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
