  <tr>
    <td align="center" style="font-weight:bold;">Please read the following guidelines carefully</td>
  <tr>
  <tr>
    <td>
      <ol>
        <li>You are required to input the Test Form number.</li>
        <li>There are 14 groups of questions in this test, each group contains 20 questions. All questions carry equal marks.</li>
        <li>Choose you answer by pressing the corresponding box.  You may change your answer simply by pressing a new box. It will automatically replace you previous choice.  You can confirm your answer by pressing the NEXT QUESTION button at the bottom of the screen.</li>
        <li>You may end the examination by pressing the SUBMIT/TEST SUMMARY button at the bottom of the screen. After pressing this button, the Test Summary showing the number of answered/unanswered questions will appear with the Review Box. You can press CONFIRM END to end the test or press BACK TO START to return to the test.</li>
      </ol>
    </td>
